      <title>为缓解劳动力短缺，迪尔公司将无人驾驶技术推广至中西部农场以外地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/deere-goes-driverless-beyond-midwest-farms-to-ease-labor-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰迪尔公司已将无人驾驶犁机引入中西部的农田，目前该公司希望将自动驾驶机器引入果园、采石场和草坪，以帮助缓解劳动力市场的紧张局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/deere-goes-driverless-beyond-midwest-farms-to-ease-labor-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 18:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
